#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.176"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.176:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.176:0.2"
msgid "18. Upāsakavagga "
msgstr "18. A Lay Follower "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.176:0.3"
msgid "176. Pītisutta "
msgstr "176. Rapture "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.176:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati pañcamattehi upāsakasatehi parivuto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika, escorted by around five hundred lay followers, went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.207, sc2
msgctxt "an5.176:2.1"
msgid "“Tumhe kho, gahapati, bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhitā cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena. "
msgstr "“Householders, you have supplied the mendicant Saṅgha with robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick. "

msgctxt "an5.176:2.2"
msgid "Na kho, gahapati, tāvatakeneva tuṭṭhi karaṇīyā: "
msgstr "But you should not be content with just this much. "

msgctxt "an5.176:2.3"
msgid "‘mayaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhitā cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārenā’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.176:2.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "an5.176:2.5"
msgid "‘kinti mayaṃ kālena kālaṃ pavivekaṃ pītiṃ upasampajja vihareyyāmā’ti. "
msgstr "‘How can we, from time to time, enter and dwell in the rapture of seclusion?’ "

msgctxt "an5.176:2.6"
msgid "Evañhi vo, gahapati, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an5.176:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā sāriputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, Venerable Sāriputta said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.2"
msgid "“acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante. "
msgstr "“It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing! "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.3"
msgid "Yāva subhāsitañcidaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā: "
msgstr "How well said this was by the Buddha: "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.4"
msgid "‘tumhe kho, gahapati, bhikkhusaṃghaṃ paccupaṭṭhitā cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena. "
msgstr "‘Householders, you have supplied the mendicant Saṅgha with robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick. "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.5"
msgid "Na kho, gahapati, tāvatakeneva tuṭṭhi karaṇīyā—"
msgstr "But you should not be content with just this much. "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.6"
msgid "mayaṃ bhikkhusaṃghaṃ paccupaṭṭhitā cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārenāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.7"
msgid "Tasmātiha, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ—"
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.8"
msgid "kinti mayaṃ kālena kālaṃ pavivekaṃ pītiṃ upasampajja vihareyyāmāti. "
msgstr "“How can we, from time to time, enter and dwell in the rapture of seclusion?” "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.9"
msgid "Evañhi vo, gahapati, sikkhitabban’ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.176:3.10"
msgid "Yasmiṃ, bhante, samaye ariyasāvako pavivekaṃ pītiṃ upasampajja viharati, pañcassa ṭhānāni tasmiṃ samaye na honti. "
msgstr "At a time when a noble disciple enters and dwells in the rapture of seclusion, five things aren’t present in him. "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.11"
msgid "Yampissa kāmūpasaṃhitaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pain and sadness connected with sensual pleasures. "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.12"
msgid "Yampissa kāmūpasaṃhitaṃ sukhaṃ somanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pleasure and happiness connected with sensual pleasures. "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.13"
msgid "Yampissa akusalūpasaṃhitaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pain and sadness connected with the unskillful. "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.14"
msgid "Yampissa akusalūpasaṃhitaṃ sukhaṃ somanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pleasure and happiness connected with the unskillful. "

msgctxt "an5.176:3.15"
msgid "Yampissa kusalūpasaṃhitaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pain and sadness connected with the skillful. "

#. VAR: imānissa pañca → imāni pañcassa (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.176:3.16"
msgid "Yasmiṃ, bhante, samaye ariyasāvako pavivekaṃ pītiṃ upasampajja viharati, imānissa pañca ṭhānāni tasmiṃ samaye na hontī”ti. "
msgstr "At a time when a noble disciple enters and dwells in the rapture of seclusion, these five things aren’t present in him.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.208, sc4
msgctxt "an5.176:4.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta. "
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta! "

msgctxt "an5.176:4.2"
msgid "Yasmiṃ, sāriputta, samaye ariyasāvako pavivekaṃ pītiṃ upasampajja viharati, pañcassa ṭhānāni tasmiṃ samaye na honti. "
msgstr "At a time when a noble disciple enters and dwells in the rapture of seclusion, five things aren’t present in him. "

msgctxt "an5.176:4.3"
msgid "Yampissa kāmūpasaṃhitaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pain and sadness connected with sensual pleasures. "

msgctxt "an5.176:4.4"
msgid "Yampissa kāmūpasaṃhitaṃ sukhaṃ somanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pleasure and happiness connected with sensual pleasures. "

msgctxt "an5.176:4.5"
msgid "Yampissa akusalūpasaṃhitaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pain and sadness connected with the unskillful. "

msgctxt "an5.176:4.6"
msgid "Yampissa akusalūpasaṃhitaṃ sukhaṃ somanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pleasure and happiness connected with the unskillful. "

msgctxt "an5.176:4.7"
msgid "Yampissa kusalūpasaṃhitaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ, tampissa tasmiṃ samaye na hoti. "
msgstr "The pain and sadness connected with the skillful. "

#. VAR: imānissa → imāni pañcassa (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.176:4.8"
msgid "Yasmiṃ, sāriputta, samaye ariyasāvako pavivekaṃ pītiṃ upasampajja viharati, imānissa pañca ṭhānāni tasmiṃ samaye na hontī”ti. "
msgstr "At a time when a noble disciple enters and dwells in the rapture of seclusion, these five things aren’t present in him.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.176:4.9"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

